todos.name: TodoTable.com
todos.description: This simple app provides you endless virtual table where you can "stick" your notes.

todos.name: Cheatsheat
todos.description:
Text can be **bold** or *italic*.

# heading 1
## heading 2
### heading 3

1) Item
2) Item

- item
- item

You can use [Markdown syntax](https://github.com/adam-p/markdown-here/wiki/Markdown-Cheatsheet)


---


- Click anywhere and create new card...
- ...or click on existing card to edit it.
- You can drag every card.
- You can drag whole table.
- You can use browser buttons [←] [→]
- You can copy&paste url and set it anywere eg. Facebook.
- You can hover every card or any empty place and start writing immediately.
- When you are hovering a card you can delete it by pressing [Delete].
